com.langtoun.oastypes.visitor

Interface OASTypeVisitor<T,C>

  • Type Parameters:
    T - The type of the objects returned from the visitor.
    C - The type of the context object that is passed to the visitor.
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    OASTypeToXmlSchemaVisitor

    public interface OASTypeVisitor<T,C>
    A visitor interface that defines methods for each of the types derived from OASType.
